snippet.title: Session: Skate Sim | Schoolyard DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to vibe in the ultimate skate playground, where every rail, ledge, and gap is primed for epic tricks and sick lines on the Schoolyard!

From grinding down stair sets to catching air off the ramps, it's all about that authentic schoolyard vibe in the new DLC Session: Skate Sim! 

Don't sleep on it, the Schoolyard is available NOW on PS5, PS4, XBOX Series, XBOX One and PC (Steam & Epic)
